1
00:00:04,050 --> 00:00:06,999
♫   Nowhere to escape   ♫

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:09,959
♫   No one to rely on   ♫

3
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:14,030
♫   Withdrawing smiles   ♫

4
00:00:15,860 --> 00:00:18,770
♫   Never give in   ♫

5
00:00:18,770 --> 00:00:23,950
♫   Forget about one's youth   ♫

6
00:00:25,850 --> 00:00:28,819
♫   I've never been afraid of loneliness when 
 embarking on this journey   ♫

7
00:00:28,819 --> 00:00:31,689
♫   Tears and regrets go hand in hand   ♫

8
00:00:31,689 --> 00:00:34,689
♫  But my heart is still fiery-hot  ♫

9
00:00:34,689 --> 00:00:37,639
♫  To the distance  ♫

10
00:00:37,639 --> 00:00:40,710
♫  The miserable past is like a dagger  ♫

11
00:00:40,710 --> 00:00:43,619
♫  Though my wings are broken  ♫

12
00:00:43,619 --> 00:00:50,240
♫  I will keep flying  ♫

13
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:56,199
♫  Following the direction of the light  ♫

14
00:00:56,199 --> 00:00:58,359
♫  I'll forget you  ♫

15
00:00:58,360 --> 00:01:04,280
♫  The memory shaped my stubbornness  ♫

16
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:07,359
♫  By virtue of the light in the dark night  ♫

17
00:01:07,359 --> 00:01:10,309
♫  I'll return it with a long ballad  ♫

18
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:12,370
♫  The river of life is under my feet  ♫

19
00:01:12,370 --> 00:01:17,560
♫  I don't regret my craziness  ♫

20
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:32,780
   

21
00:01:32,780 --> 00:01:36,260
   

22
00:01:38,380 --> 00:01:41,120
General, the water is ready.

23
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,818
Su Yishe and Nu'er are exploring the way ahead.

24
00:01:42,818 --> 00:01:46,839
And found substitutes for us to head for the grassland through the pass.

25
00:01:46,839 --> 00:01:49,159
But according to our speed now,

26
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:52,120
it will take us half a month to get to Youzhou.

27
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,599
Half a month?

28
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:55,199
Half a month will be too long.

29
00:01:55,199 --> 00:01:58,098
- We have to hurry up. 
 - Yes.

30
00:02:02,140 --> 00:02:03,740
That is...

31
00:02:05,180 --> 00:02:07,899
How could there be a dead body?

32
00:02:10,020 --> 00:02:16,960
 Timing and Subtitles by The Ode to Love Team @Viki.com 

33
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:23,420
Why is it him again?

34
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:44,378
General, what's wrong?

35
00:02:44,378 --> 00:02:48,158
Ya Luo, find a place to stay.

36
00:02:48,158 --> 00:02:49,639
Yes.

37
00:02:52,579 --> 00:02:55,438
- General, let me carry him. 
 - No.

38
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:59,339
When did he change to a busybody?

39
00:02:59,339 --> 00:03:01,819
Hold him as if it's a treasure.

40
00:03:13,179 --> 00:03:14,999
Search carefully!

41
00:03:14,999 --> 00:03:17,259
Dead or alive, we must find the body!

42
00:03:17,259 --> 00:03:19,060
 Yes! 

43
00:03:25,739 --> 00:03:28,859
Wei Shuyu, congratulations!

44
00:03:28,859 --> 00:03:30,739
For what?

45
00:03:30,739 --> 00:03:32,719
You intercepted Li Changge yourself.

46
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:34,959
And then you took the first place to shoot her.

47
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:38,020
You made great contributions to clearing the leftover traitor.

48
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:42,799
Of course, I should tell His Highness to publicize your contribution.

49
00:03:42,799 --> 00:03:46,038
Hao Du, you are so ruthless. Are you not?

50
00:03:46,038 --> 00:03:48,319
Aren't you clear whether Changge is guilty or not?

51
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:50,219
It's not important what I am thinking.

52
00:03:50,219 --> 00:03:54,939
I just follow Father's order. What he orders is what I think.

53
00:03:54,939 --> 00:03:57,620
But, Wei Shuyu, I also have some advice for you.

54
00:03:57,620 --> 00:04:01,120
We cannot have it both ways in this world.

55
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:05,318
If you want your family, be obedient and follow my order.

56
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:21,719
General, this is where hunters take a rest.

57
00:04:21,719 --> 00:04:24,100
Few people will come.

58
00:04:24,100 --> 00:04:26,238
Take the wine bottle and medicine, and a set of clothes.

59
00:04:26,239 --> 00:04:27,639
Yes.

60
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,560
Shameless!

61
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,958
Why did you hit me?

62
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:36,938
- What are you doing? 
 - Can't you see what I am doing?

63
00:05:36,938 --> 00:05:39,000
What did you see?

64
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:42,038
You are a man. What can I see?

65
00:05:42,038 --> 00:05:44,120
Then, why are you covering your eyes?

66
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:46,079
I don't like blood.

67
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:48,300
I don't want to see your wound.

68
00:05:58,220 --> 00:06:02,100
Since you are so marvelous, then do it yourself.

69
00:06:04,940 --> 00:06:07,359
I didn't ask you for help.

70
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,720
Aliqi.

71
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:38,958
- What does it mean? 
 - Spirit Wine from the West.

72
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:51,819
Much better. Thanks!

73
00:06:51,819 --> 00:06:53,879
Are you foolish?

74
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:55,439
Bear it!

75
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:05,199
You are a real man.

76
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:06,939
Give him the medicine.

77
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,460
Don't touch me!

78
00:07:13,220 --> 00:07:15,278
Don't cry aloud like a woman!

79
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:17,798
We don't have to wait till now if we want to hurt you.

80
00:07:17,799 --> 00:07:20,799
Leave him alone. He's really ungrateful.

81
00:07:20,799 --> 00:07:22,320
Go.

82
00:07:53,019 --> 00:07:55,858
Father, what's wrong?

83
00:07:55,858 --> 00:08:00,280
Prince Qin was here just now and I scolded him.

84
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:03,759
I think he will send someone here soon,

85
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:06,400
and put me to death.

86
00:08:07,579 --> 00:08:10,098
Father, I'll prepare for the carriage now.

87
00:08:10,098 --> 00:08:12,219
Please escape to our hometown of Quyang first.

88
00:08:12,219 --> 00:08:13,639
I'll find Mr. Du now.

89
00:08:13,639 --> 00:08:19,440
Shuyu, your father is not a coward.

90
00:08:21,019 --> 00:08:22,800
But...

91
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:28,010
sorry for getting you involved.

92
00:08:36,459 --> 00:08:40,259
Father, it's my fault.

93
00:08:41,119 --> 00:08:46,059
I'm not strong enough to protect my father, nor my family.

94
00:08:51,259 --> 00:08:53,300
Stand up.

95
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:58,119
What I did has nothing to do with you.

96
00:08:58,119 --> 00:09:01,079
Today, Prince Qin came to our house,

97
00:09:01,079 --> 00:09:05,500
so he is really a broad-minded man.

98
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:09,780
If you want to work for Prince Qin,

99
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:12,180
I won't stop you.

100
00:09:12,180 --> 00:09:18,778
Father, I don't know whether it is the right choice or not.

101
00:09:25,930 --> 00:09:28,680
   

102
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:49,998
Mr. Wei, this is what His Highness asked me to deliver to you.

103
00:09:49,998 --> 00:09:52,218
Father. No!

104
00:09:52,218 --> 00:09:54,610
I'll plead to his Highness and Mr. Du.

105
00:09:54,610 --> 00:09:56,390
- Shuyu. 
 - Father!

106
00:09:56,390 --> 00:09:58,540
Accept it.

107
00:10:06,780 --> 00:10:10,280
Mr. Wei, please enjoy.

108
00:10:20,379 --> 00:10:22,839
Father. Father, no!

109
00:10:22,839 --> 00:10:26,239
I'll plead to His Highness and Mr. Du.

110
00:10:26,239 --> 00:10:32,159
What have I taught you since you were young?

111
00:10:32,779 --> 00:10:34,579
Take off your hands.

112
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:47,340
Vinegar celery.

113
00:10:52,579 --> 00:10:56,079
 Advisor Fang always says that Mr. Wei loves vinegar celery. 

114
00:10:56,079 --> 00:10:59,840
 Crown Princess Zhangsun made it with five flavors in person. 

115
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:02,259
 Just to show my gratitude. 

116
00:11:02,259 --> 00:11:04,018
 Today it was my fault. 

117
00:11:04,018 --> 00:11:07,099
 Please forgive me. 

118
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:11,739
F-Father.

119
00:11:12,679 --> 00:11:13,960
Father!

120
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:15,759
Father! No!

121
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:20,659
Fa...

122
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:35,379
I was too narrow-minded.

123
00:11:35,379 --> 00:11:39,880
But Prince Qin knows when to yield and when not.

124
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,979
Although we are from different sides,

125
00:11:42,979 --> 00:11:46,180
I never say it out, but I am clear in mind.

126
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:48,860
Prince Qin is benevolent and generous,

127
00:11:49,340 --> 00:11:52,879
but also resolute in his decisions.

128
00:11:52,879 --> 00:11:56,919
No one can stop this mishap.

129
00:11:58,219 --> 00:12:00,118
As for my loyalty to my master,

130
00:12:00,118 --> 00:12:03,859
I can decline him for my whole life.

131
00:12:03,859 --> 00:12:08,379
But the lands we are in still belong to Great Tang.

132
00:12:08,379 --> 00:12:14,060
People here are still people of Great Tang.

133
00:12:14,060 --> 00:12:22,159
My long-cherished wish is just for repaying Great Tang.

134
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:26,199
Father, I know.

135
00:12:31,919 --> 00:12:35,900
For my whole life, I'm convinced by only a few people.

136
00:12:35,900 --> 00:12:37,980
This vinegar celery...

137
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:42,780
has convinced me!

138
00:13:22,339 --> 00:13:24,539
Thanks.

139
00:13:24,539 --> 00:13:26,759
I misunderstood you earlier.

140
00:13:26,759 --> 00:13:31,359
- You saved my life, I will— 
 - No need for it.

141
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:35,058
You don't owe me anything. There's nothing between us.

142
00:13:37,659 --> 00:13:39,559
That would be good.

143
00:13:42,740 --> 00:13:47,780
Well... Can I have a sip of this wine?

144
00:13:47,780 --> 00:13:49,840
Yes,

145
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:52,060
but I never suffer any loss in business.

146
00:13:52,060 --> 00:13:55,259
Why not make an exchange? I can give you the wine.

147
00:13:55,259 --> 00:13:58,439
You need to answer my questions. What do you think?

148
00:13:59,039 --> 00:14:00,678
It is impolite not to reciprocate.

149
00:14:00,679 --> 00:14:03,599
Then let's play a game. Do you dare?

150
00:14:03,599 --> 00:14:05,880
Of course.

151
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:10,299
We ask each other questions in turn.

152
00:14:10,299 --> 00:14:13,219
If one can not answer, then one should drink as a forfeit.

153
00:14:13,219 --> 00:14:14,759
Okay.

154
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:27,959
Go ahead.

155
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:31,579
Where did you get the wound on your shoulder?

156
00:14:31,579 --> 00:14:33,680
Soldiers from the court shot me.

157
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:35,299
You are so straightforward.

158
00:14:35,299 --> 00:14:38,939
Since it's an exchange, no one is allowed to lie.

159
00:14:38,939 --> 00:14:41,000
My turn.

160
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:43,358
What's your name?

161
00:14:43,359 --> 00:14:46,239
Surname, Qin. Zhun.

162
00:14:46,239 --> 00:14:48,100
You can call me A'Zhun.

163
00:14:48,100 --> 00:14:49,800
A'Zhun...

164
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,440
You?

165
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:53,579
Surname, Li. I was the 14th child in the family.

166
00:14:53,579 --> 00:14:56,019
Call me Shisi.

167
00:14:56,019 --> 00:14:59,379
Why did you want my dagger?

168
00:14:59,379 --> 00:15:02,379
I just wanted to embarrass you.

169
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:05,699
I knew you were a bad guy.

170
00:15:06,679 --> 00:15:07,999
A'Zhun, where are you from?

171
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:11,000
I'm from the central plains; born beyond the Great Wall.

172
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:13,539
- Then, where's your home? 
 - That's another question.

173
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:16,520
Next,

174
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:19,000
where are you planning to go?

175
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:24,200
To take revenge.

176
00:15:25,300 --> 00:15:28,780
Then, what about you?

177
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:31,799
To the north. Revenge for what?

178
00:15:42,479 --> 00:15:46,220
- What to do in the north? 
 - A huge business.

179
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:52,819
Since you have answered it, why did you take a drink?

180
00:15:52,819 --> 00:15:56,939
Because you will ask me about the business,

181
00:15:56,939 --> 00:15:58,680
and I cannot answer.

182
00:16:03,899 --> 00:16:06,740
I will be drunk if I keep drinking.

183
00:16:08,559 --> 00:16:11,180
Then the last question.

184
00:16:13,159 --> 00:16:16,800
Are you really called A'Zhun?

185
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:21,399
Then, Shisi,

186
00:16:21,399 --> 00:16:23,599
are you really Shisi?

187
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:38,398
 - Good! Cheers! 
 - Come on! 

188
00:16:38,398 --> 00:16:40,599
 - Again! 
 - Drink! 

189
00:16:43,579 --> 00:16:45,920
What is General talking with him?

190
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:48,299
I've not heard a laugh like that from him in a long time.

191
00:16:48,299 --> 00:16:50,479
General has been leading Eagle Division for years,

192
00:16:50,479 --> 00:16:52,419
but Great Khan is always suspicious of him.

193
00:16:52,419 --> 00:16:55,158
And he always got impeded by that deadly foe.

194
00:16:55,159 --> 00:16:57,079
Under such a situation,

195
00:16:57,079 --> 00:16:59,939
if it were you, could you laugh?

196
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:01,959
Yes, you are right.

197
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:06,219
But never mind that, don't be upset by that.

198
00:17:07,860 --> 00:17:12,059
But I haven't seen him caring about anyone so much.

199
00:17:14,830 --> 00:17:17,750
   

200
00:17:27,660 --> 00:17:29,360
Your Highness,

201
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:33,900
Princess Yongning has nothing to do with the rumor.

202
00:17:33,900 --> 00:17:36,719
It seems that it was done by others.

203
00:17:36,719 --> 00:17:42,758
As for Princess Yongning, it was my fault to let her escape.

204
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,600
Fine.

205
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:50,900
These days, massive forces have already yielded surrender.

206
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:54,119
Even if she has any movement, it won't cause big trouble.

207
00:17:54,119 --> 00:17:56,199
Just pay more attention to her.

208
00:17:56,199 --> 00:17:57,819
Yes.

209
00:17:58,479 --> 00:18:00,779
Keming.

210
00:18:00,779 --> 00:18:04,439
Do you need anything else, Your Highness?

211
00:18:22,300 --> 00:18:25,340
What Changge took away with her,

212
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:27,660
is an important item of the court.

213
00:18:27,660 --> 00:18:30,000
No matter what,

214
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:32,900
no one can keep it.

215
00:18:33,860 --> 00:18:35,940
I understand.

216
00:18:48,060 --> 00:18:50,659
 Wei Zheng was right. 

217
00:18:50,659 --> 00:18:55,019
 I'm the most ruthless person in this world. 

218
00:19:05,660 --> 00:19:08,359
- Princess. 
 - Mr. Du.

219
00:19:08,359 --> 00:19:11,619
His Highness is in there. You can go in.

220
00:19:48,520 --> 00:19:50,020
General.

221
00:19:50,020 --> 00:19:51,700
Let's set off.

222
00:19:53,239 --> 00:19:55,798
- Where is that boy? 
 - He's gone.

223
00:19:55,798 --> 00:19:57,539
Gone?

224
00:19:58,439 --> 00:20:00,699
Why didn't he say anything and just left?

225
00:20:00,760 --> 00:20:04,160
Su Yishe, send a scout back to the Eagle Division.

226
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:06,839
Ask them to prepare these, and wait for me outside You State,

227
00:20:06,839 --> 00:20:10,800
and hand this to Great Khan.

228
00:20:10,800 --> 00:20:11,819
Don't worry, General.

229
00:20:11,819 --> 00:20:13,319
Go.

230
00:20:20,619 --> 00:20:24,600
General, what should we do after we get You State?

231
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:29,259
I've already asked Su Yishe to prepare the road stone.

232
00:20:32,340 --> 00:20:35,760
   

233
00:20:41,739 --> 00:20:45,260
Greetings, Father.

234
00:20:45,260 --> 00:20:47,680
It's hard for you to see me yourself.

235
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:49,480
Did anything happen?

236
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:51,200
Nothing.

237
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:54,379
I just want to come to see you.

238
00:20:54,379 --> 00:20:55,999
That's so considerate of you.

239
00:20:55,999 --> 00:20:58,879
If nothing is wrong, just go back and have some rest.

240
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:01,920
I still have some business to handle.

241
00:21:08,019 --> 00:21:14,020
I want to ask you... about Changge.

242
00:21:16,879 --> 00:21:19,120
Please don't harm her.

243
00:21:19,120 --> 00:21:21,238
Changge just has a bad temper.

244
00:21:21,238 --> 00:21:23,039
- But she— 
 - Yan'er.

245
00:21:35,059 --> 00:21:36,759
Yan'er,

246
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:42,720
forget that Changge exists in this world.

247
00:21:43,260 --> 00:21:47,219
It's good for both you and her.

248
00:21:47,219 --> 00:21:49,099
Father!

249
00:21:49,959 --> 00:21:51,879
Your Highness, the court sent someone here.

250
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:53,879
He is here to see the princess.

251
00:21:58,260 --> 00:22:01,119
His Majesty heard that the princess harbors great righteousness in mind,

252
00:22:01,119 --> 00:22:02,459
and would love to marry into the grassland.

253
00:22:02,459 --> 00:22:06,079
I am here to send rewards and the imperial edict.

254
00:22:06,079 --> 00:22:08,800
Please accept it, Princess.

255
00:22:21,139 --> 00:22:25,338
Crown Prince's daughter, young and quiet,

256
00:22:25,338 --> 00:22:26,858
as one of the members of the royal family,

257
00:22:26,858 --> 00:22:30,239
all your reward is according to the regime.

258
00:22:30,239 --> 00:22:32,179
Now you are Royal Princess Yongan,

259
00:22:32,179 --> 00:22:33,879
you can get the rewards of 3,000 households,

260
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:36,660
and this is executed at once.

261
00:22:44,459 --> 00:22:48,018
Noble Princess Yongan, hurry and accept it!

262
00:22:52,040 --> 00:22:53,980
I accept it with pleasure.

263
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:56,339
Thanks to Your Majesty!

264
00:23:22,199 --> 00:23:26,800
I still have to marry into the grassland, right?

265
00:23:33,340 --> 00:23:35,940
   

266
00:23:52,839 --> 00:23:56,939
