 Next. 

388
00:33:05,980 --> 00:33:07,580
 Go. 

389
00:33:08,540 --> 00:33:09,819
 Okay, okay!  Go. 

390
00:33:09,819 --> 00:33:11,480
 Okay. 

391
00:33:12,019 --> 00:33:13,620
 Next. 

392
00:33:15,560 --> 00:33:16,459
 Go. 

393
00:33:16,459 --> 00:33:18,059
 Thanks. 

394
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:22,119
What's in your carriage?

395
00:33:22,119 --> 00:33:23,238
They are all grains.

396
00:33:23,238 --> 00:33:24,319
- Grains? 
 - Yes.

397
00:33:24,319 --> 00:33:26,379
You. You. Go and search.

398
00:33:26,379 --> 00:33:28,079
Yes!

399
00:33:31,139 --> 00:33:33,539
No... No need to search. Just some grains.

400
00:33:33,539 --> 00:33:36,540
It's not up to you.

401
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:42,459
Any problems?

402
00:33:42,459 --> 00:33:43,419
No.

403
00:33:43,419 --> 00:33:45,419
Okay.

404
00:33:45,419 --> 00:33:46,639
- Thanks! 
 - Go. 
 - Thanks!

405
00:33:46,639 --> 00:33:48,159
Go!  Let's go.

406
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:49,960
Wait!

407
00:33:56,099 --> 00:33:58,099
Sir.

408
00:33:58,099 --> 00:33:59,619
Why are you so nervous?

409
00:33:59,619 --> 00:34:01,219
No, Sir.

410
00:34:01,219 --> 00:34:02,859
What's in here?

411
00:34:02,859 --> 00:34:06,000
Officer, just some grains.

412
00:34:10,659 --> 00:34:12,959
Sir...

413
00:34:19,439 --> 00:34:20,539
Open it and search.

414
00:34:20,539 --> 00:34:22,639
Yes!  Yes!

415
00:34:22,639 --> 00:34:24,139
No...

416
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:49,418
- Take them all. 
 - Yes!

417
00:34:49,418 --> 00:34:51,520
No, no, no... No, sir!

418
00:34:51,520 --> 00:34:54,779
 - Go, go.  
 - I'm wronged, sir! Wronged!

419
00:34:57,220 --> 00:35:00,820
General, what's that?

420
00:35:00,820 --> 00:35:02,858
Today we didn't find anything

421
00:35:02,858 --> 00:35:05,338
and you didn't see anything. Remember?

422
00:35:05,338 --> 00:35:06,939
Yes!

423
00:35:09,940 --> 00:35:12,139
I was wronged! Officer!

424
00:35:12,139 --> 00:35:13,960
Go quickly!

425
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:16,679
I was wronged! Officer!

426
00:35:22,719 --> 00:35:25,239
- Thanks. Thanks! 
 - You're welcome.

427
00:35:29,080 --> 00:35:31,458
Master, you're so clever.

428
00:35:31,458 --> 00:35:34,918
If we didn't get on this carriage, how could we get here so quickly?

429
00:35:34,918 --> 00:35:37,259
There would be many blisters on our feet.

430
00:35:37,259 --> 00:35:40,259
This is leveraging. Learn from it.

431
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:51,919
 Their food is quite good! 

432
00:35:51,919 --> 00:35:54,379
 Slow down, Madam! 

433
00:35:54,379 --> 00:35:55,918
 What will we do next? 

434
00:35:55,919 --> 00:35:57,819
 - Wander around. 
 - Okay, let's go! 

435
00:35:57,819 --> 00:35:59,680
Let's stay here.

436
00:36:02,180 --> 00:36:03,800
- Please. 
 - Waiter?

437
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:05,519
Here!

438
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:09,279
Two gentlemen, which room do you want?

439
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:12,260
The cheapest?

440
00:36:12,260 --> 00:36:13,918
The cheapest.

441
00:36:13,919 --> 00:36:16,118
This way. Go.

442
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:19,859
Please.

443
00:36:21,160 --> 00:36:22,519
Have a look here.

444
00:36:22,520 --> 00:36:24,359
Although our room is not big,

445
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:26,278
