446
00:36:26,278 --> 00:36:27,918
Besides, it's quiet here.

447
00:36:27,919 --> 00:36:30,039
Are you satisfied, client?

448
00:36:30,039 --> 00:36:31,499
Yes.

449
00:36:31,499 --> 00:36:33,280
Okay, have some rest first.

450
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:35,760
And I will prepare the hot water for you.

451
00:36:39,700 --> 00:36:42,718
I will explore around Governor Manor. You stay here.

452
00:36:42,718 --> 00:36:44,479
Don't expose yourself.

453
00:36:44,479 --> 00:36:46,060
Yes.

454
