456
00:37:02,399 --> 00:37:03,600
I will clean it up.

457
00:37:03,600 --> 00:37:05,999
And make it a cozy place for you to have a rest.

458
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:08,198
A'Dou, don't be too tired.

459
00:37:08,199 --> 00:37:09,519
I'm okay with that.

460
00:37:09,519 --> 00:37:12,199
I'm not tired, Master. Have some rest now! Rest now!

461
00:37:12,199 --> 00:37:14,239
Nothing, I will explore a little bit.

462
00:37:14,239 --> 00:37:16,020
Master, I will follow you.

463
00:37:16,020 --> 00:37:18,859
You are just a little boy, it'd be strange for you to go with me.

464
00:37:18,859 --> 00:37:21,659
Sleep early. I'll bring you some food.

