474
00:38:25,919 --> 00:38:27,478
And head to different places.

475
00:38:27,479 --> 00:38:29,880
All good things must come to an end.

476
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:32,659
No one can stay with each other for their whole life.

477
00:38:32,659 --> 00:38:35,399
Brother Shuyu, I understand.

478
